title: Sony Vegas Pro 13.0.290 x64 Portable ---------[JUHAX69X]
description:
Sony Vegas Pro 13.0.290 x64 Portable
 
 
 

Designed for complete creative control
Vegas Pro 13 is a contemporary NLE designed for complete creative control. New features
include advanced archival tools, sophisticated audio metering, and the Vegas Pro Connect
mobile iPad companion app. Vegas Pro 13 comes complete with DVD Architect Pro 6, Dolby
Digital Professional Encoder and plug-in collections from FXHOME, NewBlueFX, and iZotope.
 
What's new in Vegas Pro 13
Vegas Pro 13 takes giant steps toward making the total multimedia creation experience faster
and easier than ever. In addition to technological advancements that span the production process
from ingesting to editing to archiving, the Vegas Pro Connect iPad app provides several truly unique collaborative
review process options that elevate client and team member participation to an entirely new level.
 
Full review and details in Homepage: sonycreativesoftware[dot]com
 
 
 
Portable:
No installation needed. Extract 7-Zip file where ever You want and start using.
 
Preckracked:
No serials or cracks needed. Scanned with F-Secure and Malwarebytes: Clean.
 
It tries to connect to the web after startup, so I will suggest to block the access with Firewall.
 
I have just test launched this once (not actually "used" yet) and it seems to work.
 
Never update, register or participate anything, from the Help menu or the site.
